---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { CONTACT_EMAIL } from '../config';
---

<Base
  title="Privacy Policy | RecastWise"
  description="How RecastWise handles data: calculations run in your browser, we don't collect your loan details, and advertising cookies are explained here."
  path="/privacy-policy/"
>
  <div class="wrap">
    <article class="prose" style="padding-block: 2rem;">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p><em>Last updated: July 3, 2026</em></p>

      <h2>The short version</h2>
      <p>
        The numbers you enter — balance, rate, term, lump sum — are processed <strong>entirely in your browser</strong>.
        We never receive, store, or transmit your loan details. There are no accounts and no forms that collect
        personal financial information.
      </p>

      <h2>Advertising</h2>
      <p>
        RecastWise is free and supported by advertising served by Google AdSense. Google and its partners use cookies
        and similar technologies to serve ads based on your prior visits to this and other websites:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Third-party vendors, including Google, use cookies to serve ads based on your prior visits to this website or other websites.</li>
        <li>Google's advertising cookies enable it and its partners to serve ads based on your visits to this and/or other sites on the Internet.</li>
        <li>
          You may opt out of personalized advertising by visiting
          <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" rel="nofollow noopener">Google Ads Settings</a>, or opt out of
          some third-party vendors' cookies at <a href="https://www.aboutads.info" rel="nofollow noopener">www.aboutads.info</a>.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Visitors in the European Economic Area, the UK, and certain US states may see a consent message allowing them
        to choose between personalized and non-personalized ads, in line with GDPR, CCPA/CPRA and similar regulations.
      </p>

      <h2>Server logs</h2>
      <p>
        Our hosting provider (Vercel) may keep standard, short-lived technical logs (such as IP address and user agent)
        for security and reliability, as virtually all web hosts do. We do not use these to identify visitors.
      </p>

      <h2>Email</h2>
      <p>If you email us at {CONTACT_EMAIL}, we use your address only to reply. We don't add you to lists or share it.</p>

      <h2>Children</h2>
      <p>RecastWise is a general-audience site and does not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.</p>

      <h2>Changes</h2>
      <p>If this policy changes, we'll update this page and the date above.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about privacy? Email <a href={`mailto:${CONTACT_EMAIL}`}>{CONTACT_EMAIL}</a>.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</Base>
